channel.title: Can any of you read?
channel.description:
Wow, it comes to me that nobody can read, like I see "Please Help" and "Help!!!!" If you guys/gals can read, you should read the stickies.. The sticky's will help you not get warned/moderated/muted/banned.
[size=12pt]Can you guys please read the stickies.[/size]
In one of the stickies it has rules, read them. In the same one "Help" is not a valid topic name, you should include what you need help with.
Mods have any rights to lock this topic.
